Ive containted a readme inside the zip but i will list it here aswell:

Whats new in this version:
* The map is less blocky, 
* Bunkers Revamped so they aint as blocky as 1.0
* Bridges Revamped so they aint as block as 1.0
* Sides Blocked so its no longer possible to run across the gap on the edge
* Fixed Texturing as on some things it was distorted
* Fixed Blocks so you take less damage when shot at covering behind them
